direction_info.description:
数据源自2012-2023年12年间全国考研试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2012-2023年全国考研英语一和考研英语二共24套考研试卷，包括阅读、完型填空、翻译、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选全国考研考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2012-2023年12年间全国考研英语一和考研英语二试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

derivative_info_list.mean: n. 参与；参加；分享；参股

word_family.mean: v. 参与；参加；具有；带有

sense_info_list.en: a person who takes part in something

examination_example.sentence: For one trial, each <highlight>participant</highlight> was shown a pile of pens that the researcher claimed were from a previous experiment.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 在一项试验中，每个参与者都被展示了一堆笔，研究人员声称这些笔来自之前的一次实验。

examination_example.sentence: Though the <highlight>participants</highlight> didn't expect a positive experience, after they went through with the experiment, "not a single person reported having been embarrassed."
examination_example.sentence_trans: 尽管参与者并不期望会有积极的体验，但在他们完成实验后，“没有一个人表示感到尴尬”。

examination_example.sentence: They are energetic <highlight>participants</highlight> in a global economy driven by the flow of work, money and ideas.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 他们是由工作、资金和思想流动所驱动的全球经济的积极参与者。

examination_example.sentence: According to the researchers, the <highlight>participants</highlight>' phones apparently substituted for real friends.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 据研究人员称，参与者的电话显然替代了真正的朋友。

examination_example.sentence: Moving away from a focus on laboratory studies with undergraduate <highlight>participants</highlight> towards more complex, real-world situations studied with more diverse groups of people.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 从专注于与本科生一起进行的实验室研究转向由更多人群研究的更加复杂，真实的情况。

examination_example.sentence: In one experiment, nearly 200 <highlight>participants</highlight> boarded a double-decker bus for a tour of Philadelphia.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 在一项实验中，近200名参与者登上双层巴士游览费城。

direction_info.description:
数据源自2016.6-2023.6年8年间全四级试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight>考纲释义</highlight>
精选实考、考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2016-2023年51套试卷，包括阅读、听力、翻译等所有题型。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2016-2023年8年间试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

derivative_info_list.mean: n. 参与；参加；分享；参股

word_family.mean: v. 参与；参加；具有；带有

sense_info_list.en: a person who takes part in something

examination_example.sentence: What they found was that it wasn't breakfast itself that caused the <highlight>participants</highlight> to lose weight: it was changing their normal routine.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 结果发现，并不是早餐本身导致参与者减肥：而是日常饮食规律的改变。

examination_example.sentence: Most of the <highlight>participants</highlight> are people who are just walking by or are on the island for other reasons, or they just kind of happen to be there.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 大多数的活动参与者都是路过或出于其他原因来到了总督岛，要不然就是恰巧刚好在岛上。

examination_example.sentence: Each session has a theme, and <highlight>participants</highlight> are given a variety of materials and prompts and asked to cover surfaces with their thoughts and art.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 每次活动都有一个主题，参与者利用给定的各种材料和提示在墙上表达出他们的想法和艺术作品。

examination_example.sentence: <highlight>Participants</highlight> were balanced across the three groups for age, sex, educational background, severity and duration of depression, and use of antidepressants (抗抑郁药) .
examination_example.sentence_trans: 参与者在年龄、性别、教育背景、抑郁的严重程度和持续时间以及抗抑郁药的使用方面在三组之间保持平衡。

examination_example.sentence: So far, <highlight>participants</highlight> have ranged in age from 2 to 85.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 到目前为止，参与者的年龄从2岁到85岁不等。

examination_example.sentence: The <highlight>participants</highlight>' stress and anxiety levels became lower and the effects on heart rates appeared to follow suit.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 参与者的压力和焦虑水平变低，对心率的影响似乎也跟着降低。

examination_example.sentence: In one European study, <highlight>participants</highlight> listened to music as the researchers monitored their heart rates and blood pressure.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 在一项欧洲研究中，当研究人员监测他们的心率和血压时，参与者听音乐。

examination_example.sentence: Data collected from the device could be used to recognize different <highlight>participants</highlight> based on how they typed, with very low error rates.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 从该设备收集的数据可以根据不同的参与者的打字方式来识别他们，错误率非常低。
